							<h3>Privacy Policy</h3>
							<p>Wyatt itself does not collect any personal data. The application does not store any data on a server. The user's (API) key is stored securely on the client device along with the user's reminder data (that's the data entered by the user through the application's user interface). The application itself does not use cookies or any other tracking technologies.</p>
